@ECHO OFF\n:: Check for administrative privileges\nNET SESSION >NUL 2>&1\nIF %ERRORLEVEL% NEQ 0 (\n    ECHO This script requires administrative privileges.\n    ECHO Trying to restart as an administrator...\n    :: Use PowerShell to restart the script with elevated privileges\n    PowerShell -Command "Start-Process '%~f0' -Verb RunAs"\n    EXIT /B\n)\n\n:: Your original script content\nECHO Copying config file to the Windows/System32 directory...\nCOPY config.xml C:\Windows\System32\DataLinks.xml\n\nECHO Done.\nPAUSE